  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p>Inghams is delighted to have been shortlisted for the World Snow Awards 2017. Presented by The Telegraph Ski &amp; Snowboard Magazine, the prestigious World Snow Awards honour the very best in the world of skiing and snowboarding, highlighting the top performers of the past 12 months and the most promising prospects for the season to come.</p>
<p>Inghams has been nominated and shortlisted for the category of <strong>Best UK Tour Operator</strong>. The shortlist was decided by a judging panel of leading figures in the UK skiing and snowboarding industry, but the winners will be decided by the public vote.</p>
<p>Inghams is one of the UK’s most experienced specialist tour operators, founded over 80 years ago by Walter Ingham (in 1934), who loved the mountains and loved sharing his passion with others. Today, the brand continues to deliver excellent, award-winning holidays whilst understanding the importance of value for money. With the recent launch of its Ski 17/18 main edition brochure, Inghams has again extended its winter programme across Europe and Finnish Lapland, offering plenty of choice for the coming winter season and responding to the desires of the modern traveller.</p>
<p>The public vote is open until <strong>Friday 6<sup>th</sup> October 2017</strong> and the winners will be announced at <strong>The Telegraph Ski &amp; Snowboard Show</strong> at Battersea Evolution, from 26<sup>th</sup> – 29<sup>th</sup> October 2017.</p>
</div>
<div class="g12">
<p><strong>ENDS.</strong></p>
<p>For bookings, please visit <strong><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk">www.inghams.co.uk</a>, </strong>call <strong>01483 791 114.</strong></p>
<p>For PR enquiries, please contact Frankie Gibson, PR Executive, on <a href="mailto:frankie.gibson@inghams.co.uk">frankie.gibson@inghams.co.uk</a> or call <strong>01483 791 045</strong>.</p>
</div>
